Azure Databricks Cluster Configuration
Cluster Type: Standard (Interactive or Job Cluster)
Node Types:
Driver Node: Standard_DS3_v2 (14 GB memory, 4 cores)
Worker Nodes: Standard_DS3_v2 (scale as needed)
Runtime Version: Databricks Runtime 10.4 (or latest LTS version)
Autoscaling: Enabled for cost optimization (min 2 nodes, max 8 nodes).
